Package: modest
Title: Model-Based Dose Escalation Using Shiny Tools
Version: 0.1
Date: 2017-06-26
Authors@R: c(person("Philip", "Pallmann", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="p.pallmann@lancaster.ac.uk"), person("Fang", "Wan", role="aut"))
Description: User-friendly Shiny apps for designing and evaluating phase I cancer clinical trials, with the aim to estimate the maximum tolerated dose (MTD) of a novel drug, using a Bayesian logistic regression method.
